<Layout title="Investing — Sunil M Pai">
  <div class="grid layout-float">
    <div class="profile-image">
      <figure>
        <img src="/investing.jpg" alt="Sunil at a poker table" />
        <figcaption class="photo-caption">Poker at Satya's!</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
    <div class="bio">
      <h1>Investing</h1>
      <p>I began my individual investing career as a scout for Lightspeed Venture Partners. They trusted my instincts and gave me a pool of capital to invest at my sole discretion. That fund is the highest performing scout fund in the program's history.</p>
      <p>Since 2019, my angel track record is a 8x DPI (distributed 8+ times the capital originally invested) and on track to reach 17.5x when fully realized.</p>

      <p>In addition to my personal investments, I run <a href="https://www.angelcollective.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Angel Collective</a> with my partner, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/candito/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nick Candito</a>.
        I believe investing other peoples' money is a privilege and a responsibility. I think aligning incentives is a critical part of investing. While the industry average is a 1-3% GP commitment (skin-in-the-game), I commit 15%+ of my own capital alongside my investors. </p>

      <h2>Advising</h2>
      <p>I serve as a hands-on advisor to several startups:</p>
      <ul class="advising-list">
        <li class="advising-item">
          <div class="advising-description">
            <a href="https://www.akashsystems.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Akash Systems</a> — Builds energy and capital efficient AI infrastructure.
          </div>
          <div class="advising-meta">Series B · Founders Fund, Khosla Ventures</div>
        </li>
        <li class="advising-item">
          <div class="advising-description">
            <a href="https://www.athena.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Athena</a> — A human+machine assistant company.
          </div>
          <div class="advising-meta">Series A · Khosla Ventures</div>
        </li>
        <li class="advising-item">
          <div class="advising-description">
            <a href="https://daylightcomputer.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Daylight Computer</a> — A new kind of computer, designed for deep focus and wellbeing.
          </div>
          <div class="advising-meta">Series A · Lachy Groom, Dan Romero, Balaji, Claire Hughes Johnson</div>
        </li>
        <li class="advising-item">
          <div class="advising-description">
            <strong>[Stealth]</strong> — A fintech incubation launching in Summer '26.
          </div>
          <div class="advising-meta">Seed · Confidential</div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What I Look For</h2>
      <p>I love investing because I love being in dialogue with people who are at the pinnacle of their fields. I am a founder-driven investor and have invested in everything from early stage B2B SaaS to an oil refinery project in The Gambia.</p>
      <p>I like to help founders with growth/distribution, product, operational discipline, and fundraising.</p>
      <p>I work best with founders that communicate transparently, are often technical or very structured in their thinking, and operate with a high degree of agency.</p>
    </div>
